                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                                         <p class="text-justify">
We at Bonds Adda, a website of <strong>M/s Dimension Financial Solutions Private Limited</strong> follows the Code of Conduct as per the Schedule II of Securities and Exchange Board of India (Stock-Brokers) Regulations, 1992 amended from time to time. </p>
                                    </div>
